<div class="jumbotron">
  <h2>Participate in your local meetings</h2>
  <p class="lead">Click on the meeting link for a list of upcoming meetings.</p>
  <% if @current_user != nil do %>
    <p>Logged in as: <%= @current_user.email %></p>
  <% end %>
</div>

<div>
  <p class="large">The purpose of this site is to provide a list of civic meetings grouped by data and type open to the public which can be added to one's calendar.</p>

  <h3><a href="/meetings">List of Meetings</a></h3>

  <p><img class="meetings" src="/images/meeting.jpg"></p>
</div>

